## Quick Start

1. Import the official `{{ support.cube_package_label }}` drivers into `Drivers/`.
2. Open `MDK-ARM/{{ project_name }}.uvprojx` in Keil5.
3. Wire the modules according to the assignments below and review power, pull-up, and level compatibility details.
4. Build the project and flash the generated `axf` or `hex` file as needed.
5. Keep application logic in the `USER CODE` regions of `App/Src/app_main.c`.

